genresAdvancedInfo.name: classic tunisian pop
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Classic Tunisian pop is a genre of music that emerged in Tunisia in the 1960s and 1970s. It is characterized by its fusion of traditional North African rhythms and melodies with Western pop influences.
